  "response": "Here are several approaches to creating a website with a monthly subscription feature, ranging from no-code to low-code options:\n\n1. No-Code Platforms (Easiest):\n- Wix\n- Squarespace\n- Webflow\n- Bubble.io\n- Carrd\n\nPros:\n- Drag-and-drop interface\n- No coding required\n- Quick setup\n- Built-in payment integrations\n\n2. Website Builders with Payment Features:\n- Shopify\n- Kajabi\n- Kartra\n- WordPress + WooCommerce\n- Memberpress\n\nPros:\n- Ready-made subscription tools\n- Payment gateway integrations\n- Membership management\n\n3. Payment Gateway Services:\n- Stripe\n- PayPal\n- Recurly\n- Chargebee\n\nPros:\n- Powerful subscription management\n- Can integrate with various platforms\n\nRecommended Steps:\n1. Define your business model\n2. Choose a platform\n3. Select a payment gateway\n4. Design your website\n5. Set up subscription tiers\n6. Test payment process\n7. Launch and market\n\nLearning Resources:\n- YouTube tutorials\n- Udemy courses\n- Platform-specific documentation\n- Online web development communities\n\nRecommendation for beginners: Start with Wix or Squarespace for simplicity.",
